{
  "video_id": "64fDIZiV-SM",
  "title": "Shake up your story | Raghava KK",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 15260.0,
      "end_time": 17259.0,
      "text": "Hi everyone."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 17260.0,
      "end_time": 20260.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m an artist and a dad -- second time around."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 20260.0,
      "end_time": 22260.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 22260.0,
      "end_time": 25260.0,
      "text": "And I want to share with you my latest art project."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 25260.0,
      "end_time": 28260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a children&#39;s book for the iPad."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 28260.0,
      "end_time": 30260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a little quirky and silly."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 30260.0,
      "end_time": 32260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s called \"Pop-It,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 32259.0,
      "end_time": 35260.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s about the things little kids do with their parents."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 35260.0,
      "end_time": 37260.0,
      "text": "(Music)"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 37260.0,
      "end_time": 39260.0,
      "text": "So this is about potty training --"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 39260.0,
      "end_time": 42260.0,
      "text": "as most of you, I hope, know."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 42260.0,
      "end_time": 44260.0,
      "text": "You can tickle the rug."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 44260.0,
      "end_time": 46260.0,
      "text": "You can make the baby poop."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 46260.0,
      "end_time": 49260.0,
      "text": "You can do all those fun things."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 50260.0,
      "end_time": 53260.0,
      "text": "You can burst bubbles."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 54260.0,
      "end_time": 57260.0,
      "text": "You can draw, as everyone should."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 58260.0,
      "end_time": 60260.0,
      "text": "But you know, I have a problem with children&#39;s books:"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 60260.0,
      "end_time": 62260.0,
      "text": "I think they&#39;re full of propaganda."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 62260.0,
      "end_time": 65259.0,
      "text": "At least an Indian trying to get one of these American books in Park Slope, forget it."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 65260.00000000001,
      "end_time": 68260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not the way I was brought up."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 68260.0,
      "end_time": 70260.0,
      "text": "So I said, \"I&#39;m going to counter this with my own propaganda.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 70260.0,
      "end_time": 72260.0,
      "text": "If you notice carefully,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 72260.0,
      "end_time": 75260.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s a homosexual couple bringing up a child."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 75260.0,
      "end_time": 77260.0,
      "text": "You don&#39;t like it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 77260.0,
      "end_time": 80260.0,
      "text": "Shake it, and you have a lesbian couple."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 80260.0,
      "end_time": 82260.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 82260.0,
      "end_time": 86260.0,
      "text": "Shake it, and you have a heterosexual couple."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 86260.0,
      "end_time": 89260.0,
      "text": "You know, I don&#39;t even believe in the concept of an ideal family."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 89260.0,
      "end_time": 91260.0,
      "text": "I have to tell you about my childhood."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 91260.0,
      "end_time": 94260.0,
      "text": "I went to this very proper Christian school"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 94260.0,
      "end_time": 97260.0,
      "text": "taught by nuns, fathers, brothers, sisters."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 97260.0,
      "end_time": 99260.0,
      "text": "Basically, I was brought up to be a good Samaritan,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 99260.0,
      "end_time": 101260.0,
      "text": "and I am."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 101260.0,
      "end_time": 104260.0,
      "text": "And I&#39;d go at the end of the day to a traditional Hindu house,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 104260.0,
      "end_time": 106260.0,
      "text": "which was probably the only Hindu house"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 106260.0,
      "end_time": 109260.0,
      "text": "in a predominantly Islamic neighborhood."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 110260.0,
      "end_time": 113260.0,
      "text": "Basically, I celebrated every religious function."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 113260.0,
      "end_time": 116260.0,
      "text": "In fact, when there was a wedding in our neighborhood,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 116260.0,
      "end_time": 118260.0,
      "text": "all of us would paint our houses for the wedding."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 118260.0,
      "end_time": 120260.0,
      "text": "I remember we cried profusely"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 120260.0,
      "end_time": 122260.0,
      "text": "when the little goats we played with in the summer"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 122260.0,
      "end_time": 124260.0,
      "text": "became biriani."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 124260.0,
      "end_time": 126260.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 126260.0,
      "end_time": 128259.0,
      "text": "We all had to fast during Ramadan."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 128258.99999999999,
      "end_time": 130258.99999999999,
      "text": "It was a very beautiful time."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 130258.99999999999,
      "end_time": 132260.0,
      "text": "But I must say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 132260.0,
      "end_time": 135260.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ll never forget, when I was 13 years old, this happened."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 135260.0,
      "end_time": 137260.0,
      "text": "Babri Masjid --"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 137260.0,
      "end_time": 139260.0,
      "text": "one of the most beautiful mosques in India,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 139260.0,
      "end_time": 142260.0,
      "text": "built by King Babur, I think, in the 16th century --"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 142260.0,
      "end_time": 144260.0,
      "text": "was demolished by Hindu activists."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 144260.0,
      "end_time": 146260.0,
      "text": "This caused major riots in my city."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 146260.0,
      "end_time": 148260.0,
      "text": "And for the first time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 148260.0,
      "end_time": 150260.0,
      "text": "I was affected"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 150260.0,
      "end_time": 152260.0,
      "text": "by this communal unrest."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 152260.0,
      "end_time": 154260.0,
      "text": "My little five-year-old kid neighbor"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 154260.0,
      "end_time": 156260.0,
      "text": "comes running in,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 156260.0,
      "end_time": 159260.0,
      "text": "and he says, \"Rags, Rags."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 159260.0,
      "end_time": 162260.0,
      "text": "You know the Hindus are killing us Muslims. Be careful.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 162260.0,
      "end_time": 164260.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m like, \"Dude, I&#39;m Hindu.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 164260.0,
      "end_time": 165260.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 165260.0,
      "end_time": 168260.0,
      "text": "He&#39;s like, \"Huh!\""
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 168260.0,
      "end_time": 171260.0,
      "text": "You know, my work is inspired"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 171260.0,
      "end_time": 173260.0,
      "text": "by events such as this."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 173260.0,
      "end_time": 175260.0,
      "text": "Even in my gallery shows,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 175260.0,
      "end_time": 177260.0,
      "text": "I try and revisit historic events"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 177260.0,
      "end_time": 179260.0,
      "text": "like Babri Masjid,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 179260.0,
      "end_time": 181260.0,
      "text": "distill only its emotional residue"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 181260.0,
      "end_time": 183260.0,
      "text": "and image my own life."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 183260.0,
      "end_time": 185260.0,
      "text": "Imagine history being taught differently."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 185260.0,
      "end_time": 186260.0,
      "text": "Remember that children&#39;s book"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 186260.0,
      "end_time": 189260.0,
      "text": "where you shake and the sexuality of the parents change?"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 189260.0,
      "end_time": 190260.0,
      "text": "I have another idea."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 190260.0,
      "end_time": 193260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a children&#39;s book about Indian independence --"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 193260.0,
      "end_time": 195260.0,
      "text": "very patriotic."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 195260.0,
      "end_time": 197260.0,
      "text": "But when you shake it, you get Pakistan&#39;s perspective."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 197260.0,
      "end_time": 200260.0,
      "text": "Shake it again, and you get the British perspective."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 200260.0,
      "end_time": 205260.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 205260.0,
      "end_time": 207260.0,
      "text": "You have to separate fact from bias, right."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 207260.0,
      "end_time": 209260.0,
      "text": "Even my books on children"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 209260.0,
      "end_time": 211260.0,
      "text": "have cute, fuzzy animals."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 211260.0,
      "end_time": 213260.0,
      "text": "But they&#39;re playing geopolitics."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 213260.0,
      "end_time": 215260.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re playing out Israel-Palestine,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 215260.0,
      "end_time": 217260.0,
      "text": "India-Pakistan."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 217260.0,
      "end_time": 219260.0,
      "text": "You know, I&#39;m making a very important argument."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 219260.0,
      "end_time": 221260.0,
      "text": "And my argument [is]"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 221260.0,
      "end_time": 225260.0,
      "text": "that the only way for us to teach creativity"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 225260.0,
      "end_time": 227260.0,
      "text": "is by teaching children perspectives"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 227260.0,
      "end_time": 229260.0,
      "text": "at the earliest stage."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 229260.0,
      "end_time": 231260.0,
      "text": "After all, children&#39;s books are manuals on parenting,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 231260.0,
      "end_time": 234260.0,
      "text": "so you better give them children&#39;s books that teach them perspectives."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 234260.0,
      "end_time": 236260.0,
      "text": "And conversely,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 236260.0,
      "end_time": 238260.0,
      "text": "only when you teach perspectives"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 238260.0,
      "end_time": 240260.0,
      "text": "will a child be able to imagine"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 240260.0,
      "end_time": 242260.0,
      "text": "and put themselves in the shoes"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 242260.0,
      "end_time": 244260.0,
      "text": "of someone who is different from them."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 244260.0,
      "end_time": 246260.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m making an argument that art and creativity"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 246260.0,
      "end_time": 249260.0,
      "text": "are very essential tools in empathy."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 249260.0,
      "end_time": 251260.0,
      "text": "You know, I can&#39;t promise my child"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 251260.0,
      "end_time": 253260.0,
      "text": "a life without bias --"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 253260.0,
      "end_time": 255260.0,
      "text": "we&#39;re all biased --"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 255260.0,
      "end_time": 258260.0,
      "text": "but I promise to bias my child with multiple perspectives."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 258260.0,
      "end_time": 260260.0,
      "text": "Thank you very much."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 260260.0,
      "end_time": 264260.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}